reviews.text: Situated right at the upper fringes of Wong Tai Sin, this restaurant serves a great variety of excellent noodle dishes. The fish dumpling and their wonton is a must try. Not to be overlooked, their chilli is fantastic. They actually sell the chilli and other ingredients for the hot pot too.
麵質爽滑彈牙，好吃
雲吞一流，價目公道，低食！
麵質爽口彈牙， 冇鹼水味， 餐牌上全部都好好食！ 味道唔會太濃， 良心店舖， 九龍區嘅推介
魚蛋彈牙，牛腩夠林，份量算足
